{"tid":1473193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【求再推】被遺忘嘅一群人，由612開始與大家同行 (817繼續與神同行)","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T11:12:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3b3d09bf7690244f28422d1e1283faa70c19fa","tid":1473193,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.15752-9/67939230_344364363179536_7916443059531808768_n.png?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_eui2=AeF8AGSI34P8OkPINFrVukANscADcdMp6LV7WWf29eFRKyOCeHkUHeN36DbC_mefVMtF1E9wgIDIKRYenfdfdHIiGyOMpA-YrUIKWxO2KTLp_A&amp;_nc_oc=AQnPHmeHoW14OWZvWdANPJId1qBwvvTTh4qo4fMiDr__pmwUA_H_l0xOT3uOeWCM-KQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=5ad402426199c74332814a482aed994f&amp;oe=5DD5E7D8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.15752-9%2F67939230_344364363179536_7916443059531808768_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_eui2%3DAeF8AGSI34P8OkPINFrVukANscADcdMp6LV7WWf29eFRKyOCeHkUHeN36DbC_mefVMtF1E9wgIDIKRYenfdfdHIiGyOMpA-YrUIKWxO2KTLp_A%26_nc_oc%3DAQnPHmeHoW14OWZvWdANPJId1qBwvvTTh4qo4fMiDr__pmwUA_H_l0xOT3uOeWCM-KQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D5ad402426199c74332814a482aed994f%26oe%3D5DD5E7D8&h=2d889a81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［🎶你杖扶持 你竿引領🎶］<br />\n<br />\n從6月起揭開序幕的漫長抗爭路🛤已踞於香港人之間長達一個月，人人疲憊不堪🤕<br />\n811黑夜過後，港人心中從此多了一個傷口，面對警方喬裝示威者、於地鐵站內拘捕制服離開市民、室內施放催淚彈、女急救員於無衝擊下被槍擊頭部致盲🤢、無差別打人......等等的事件，叫人對這個社會公義如何抱有希望？唯有依靠神，從中找到引領💞<br />\n今個星期，繼續有一群熱心的基督徒自發起「與神同行」唱詩活動❤️🎶<br />\n希望將詩歌帶到香港的核心&mdash;&mdash;中環「政府山」，呼喚當權者歸回上帝🗣同時驅走黑暗☀️<br />\n希望大家到場支持📣🙆🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\nChannel: <a href=\"https://t.me/walkingwithgod\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwalkingwithgod&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=767646c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/walkingwithgod</a><br />\n<br />\n日期：17-08-2019<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：19：00至22：00<br />\n         （